title: All Itchy & Scratchy episodes ever as of season.19.the.simpsons
description:
All Itchy & Scratchy episodes ever as of season 19 the Simpsons

This contains every bit of Itchy and Scratchy, ever, in the Simpsons. Single handedly spliced out by me. I watched them all in order, so the files are in roughly chronological order, numbered and tagged with an episode title if possible. All avi, in divx format. 

As some random extras, it also contains some shorts I think are funny on their own, as well as all the original Tracey Ulman show Simpsons shorts.

Enjoy. Please Seed, I wanna spread this one around like wildfire
